Package org.jhove2.module.format.sgml

Interface Summary
OnsgmlsOutputParser Interface for parsers of output of ONGSMLS, based on James Clark's OpenSP (http://www.jclark.com/sp/index.htm), which is available at SourceForge as part of the OpenJade distribution (see http://sourceforge.net/projects/openjade/).
OpenSpErrMessageParser Interface for parse of .err (Message) files produced by OpenSp onsgmls and sgmlnorm utilities
OpenSpOptions Interface for options setting for OpenSp commands.
SgmlNormParser Interface for parsing .out (normalized SGML) output of OpenSp sgmlnorm utility, in order to extract DOCTYPE statement properties
SgmlParser Interface to wrap actual parser of SGML file
 

Class Summary
AbstractOpenSpMessageParser Abstract base class for parsers of OpenSP .err (Message) files
ErrFileParser Class to parser .err (Message) files produced by OpenSp onsgmls and sgmlnorm utilities
EsisFileParser Class to parse .out (ESIS) files produced by OpenSp onsgmls module Please see module specification document for details of the ESIS file format
OnsgmlsOptions Class to contain options setting for OpenSp onsgmls command.
OpenSpWrapper Wrapper around OpenSP SGML parser and onsgmlNorm utility.
SgmlDocumentProperties Thin container for SGML document properties extracted by parser engine Allows us to free parser objects
SgmlModule JHOVE2 SGML module.
SgmlNormFileParser Class for parsing output of OpenSp sgmlnorm utility.
SgmlNormOptions Class for setting options for OpenSp sgmlnorm utility
